    "description": "Workday staffing v6 — May 15 deep dive demo collection for Alex Wang + John Yates.\n\n2 requests, 4 tests each:\n- GET /workers?search=Adam — live Workday sandbox\n- POST /workers/{id}/checkInTopics — Postman mock (token doesn't have write scope)\n\nThe tests prove the AI is reasoning about the API: contract conformance (Test 3) + behavior validation (Test 4 GET / round-trip Test 2 POST / WID format Test 3 POST).",
